resources.string: In order to ensure your normal and safe use, you need to obtain the device identification code (some mobile phones prompt to obtain the mobile phone number), please allow.

The application saves running status and other information. It needs to obtain the permission to read and write mobile phone storage (the system prompts to access photos, media content and files on the device). Please allow.

string.name: dcloud_privacy_prompt_message
string.Data:
"Please read carefully and fully understand the terms of the "Service Agreement" and "Privacy Policy", including but not limited to: In order to provide you with better services, we need to collect your device identification, operation log and other information for analysis, Optimize application performance
You can read"Service Agreement"and"Privacy Policy"Learn more. If you agree, please click the button below to start accepting our service."
